<section id="practical-info" class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-white scroll-mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-11">
      <p class="font-display italic text-gold text-lg mb-2">Good to know</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-wine tracking-tight">Practical Info</h2>
      <div class="section-rule mt-5" aria-hidden="true"><span>§</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-charcoal">

      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Babysitting</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          We&rsquo;re arranging sitters through
          <a href="https://www.gensdeconfiance.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-wine font-medium underline underline-offset-2 decoration-charcoal/20 hover:decoration-wine/60">Gens de confiance</a>
          plus on-site help at La Fabrique des Ducs for children&rsquo;s games and activities during the week and on the anniversary evening.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Shopping &amp; Essentials</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-2 leading-relaxed">
          There&rsquo;s a small supermarket in Epinac for basics. For a larger shop,
          head to <strong>Autun</strong> (20 min) which has several supermarkets (Carrefour, Lidl).
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          The local <strong>Boulangerie Royer David</strong> in Epinac opens at 6am for fresh bread
          and pastries (closed Mondays).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Stay Connected</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">
          We&rsquo;ll set up a <strong>WhatsApp group</strong> for real-time coordination
          during the week &mdash; ride sharing, dinner plans, activity sign-ups, and
          general fun. Link will be shared before the trip.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
